This follows EN 1993-1-1, Cl. Table 8.5 (Recommended values for dimple imperfection amplitude parameters $U_{n1}$ and $U_{n2}$) with supporting classification guidance from Cl. 10.1.3.4 (Purlins with semi-continuity given by overlaps or sleeves).

